@startuml
skinparam monochrome true
skinparam packageStyle rectangle
skinparam shadowing false
skinparam sequenceMessageAlign center
autonumber

actor "Pilot" as Pilot
participant ":System" as System

activate Pilot

Pilot -> System : Requests to create a flight plan from a file

activate System
System --> Pilot : Requests flight plan file and file format
deactivate System

Pilot -> System : Provides flight plan file

activate System
System --> System : Check if pilot is authenticated and authorized
System --> System : Validate file existence and readability
System --> System : Detect or validate file format
System --> System : Perform lexical analysis
System --> System : Perform syntactic analysis
System --> System : Build internal flight plan representation
System --> System : Perform semantic analysis
System --> System : Validate extracted flight plan business rules
System --> System : Set flight plan status to draft

alt file and flight plan are valid
    System --> System : Import and store flight plan
    System --> Pilot : Flight plan imported successfully
else file or flight plan is invalid
    System --> Pilot : Display meaningful validation errors
end

deactivate System
deactivate Pilot

@enduml